18 Segunda Divisi\u00f3n|2017/18]]\n|style=\"background:silver;\"|[[2017\u201318 Real Valladolid season|5th]]\n|[[Luis C\u00e9sar Sampedro]] <br />[[Sergio (footballer, born 1976)|Sergio Gonz\u00e1lez]]\n|Qualified for [[2018 Segunda Divisi\u00f3n play-offs|Promotion play-off]]<br />Promoted to [[La Liga]]\n|-\n|style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2018\u201319 La Liga|2018/19]]\n|style=\"background:gold;\" rowspan=\"2\"|1\n|style=\"background:gold;\" rowspan=\"2\"|[[La Liga|1\u00aa]]\n|style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2018\u201319 Real Valladolid season|16th]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Sergio (footballer, born 1976)|Sergio Gonz\u00e1lez]]\n|\n|-\n|style=\"background:gold;\"|[[2019\u201320 La Liga|2019/20]]\n|style=\"background:gold;\"|\n|\n|}\n\n----\n*'''42''' seasons in [[La Liga]]\n*'''34''' seasons in [[Segunda Divisi\u00f3n]]\n*'''10''' seasons in [[Tercera Divisi\u00f3n]]\n\n===European Cups history===\n====UEFA Cup====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Season\n! Round\n! Club\n! Home \n! Away\n! Aggregate\n|-\n|[[1984\u201385 UEFA Cup|1984\u201385]]\n|Round of 64\n|v. {{flagicon|YUG}} [[NK Rijeka|Rijeka]]\n|1\u20130\n|1\u20134\n|2\u20134\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[1997\u201398 UEFA Cup|1997\u201398]]\n|Round of 64\n|v. {{flagicon|LAT}} [[Skonto FC|Skonto]]\n|2\u20130\n|0\u20131\n|2\u20131\n|-\n|Round of 32\n|v. {{flagicon|RUS}} [[FC Spartak Moscow|Spartak Moscow]]\n|1\u20132\n|0\u20132\n|1\u20134\n|-\n|}\n\n====UEFA Cup Winners' Cup====\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Season\n! Round\n! Club\n! Home \n! Away\n! Aggregate\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\"|[[1989\u201390 European Cup Winners' Cup|1989\u201390]]\n|Round of 32\n|v. {{flagicon|Malta}} [[\u0126amrun Spartans F.C.|\u0126amrun Spartans]]\n|5\u20130\n|1\u20130\n|6\u20130\n|-\n|Round of 16\n|v. {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Djurg\u00e5rdens IF Fotboll|Djurg\u00e5rdens IF]]\n|2\u20130\n|2\u20132\n|4\u20132\n|-\n|Quarter-finals\n|v. {{flagicon|FRA}} [[AS Monaco FC|Monaco]]\n|0\u20130\n|0\u20130 ([[Overtime (sports)|aet]])\n|1\u20133 ([[Penalty shootout (association football)|pen.]])\n|-\n|}\n\n==Current squad==\n{{updated|31 January 2020}}.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.realvalladolid.es/primer-equipo/plantilla/|title=Primer equipo|trans-title=First team|publisher=Real Valladolid|language=Spanish|accessdate=25 June 2019}}</ref>\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no= 1|nat=ESP|name=[[Jordi Masip]]|pos=GK|other=[[Captain (association football)|3rd captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no= 2|nat=ESP|name=[[Pedro Porro]]|pos=DF|other=on loan from [[Manchester City F.C.|Manchester City]]}}\n{{Fs player|no= 3|nat=FRA|name=[[Hatem Ben Arfa]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no= 4|nat=ESP|name=[[Kiko (Spanish footballer, born 1988)|Kiko]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no= 5|nat=ESP|name=[[Javi S\u00e1nchez (footballer)|Javi S\u00e1nchez]]|pos=DF|other=on loan from [[Real Madrid CF|Real Madrid]]}}\n{{Fs player|no= 6|nat=ESP|name=[[Ra\u00fal Garc\u00eda (footballer, born 1989)|Ra\u00fal Garc\u00eda]]|pos=DF|other=on loan from [[Getafe CF|Getafe]]}}\n{{Fs player|no= 7|nat=ESP|name=[[Sergi Guardiola]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no= 8|nat=BRA|name=[[Matheus Fernandes]]|pos=MF|other=on loan from [[Sociedade Esportiva Palmeiras|Palmeiras]]}}\n{{Fs player|no= 9|nat=TUR|name=[[Enes \u00dcnal]]|pos=FW|other=on loan from [[Villarreal CF|Villarreal]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=10|nat=ESP|name=[[\u00d3scar Plano]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=11|nat=ESP|name=[[Pablo Herv\u00edas]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=13|nat=ESP|name=[[Jos\u00e9 Antonio Caro (footballer, born 1994)|Jos\u00e9 Antonio Caro]]|pos=GK}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=14|nat=ESP|name=[[Rub\u00e9n Alcaraz]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=16|nat=ESP|name=[[Fede San Emeterio]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=17|nat=ESP|name=[[Javi Moyano]]|pos=DF|other=[[Captain (association football)|captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=18|nat=ESP|name=[[Anto\u00f1ito (footballer, born 1987)|Anto\u00f1ito]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=19|nat=ESP|name=[[Toni Villa]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=20|nat=ESP|name=[[Sandro Ram\u00edrez|Sandro]]|pos=FW|other=on loan from [[Everton F.C.|Everton]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=21|nat=ESP|name=[[M\u00edchel (footballer, born 1988)|M\u00edchel]]|pos=MF|other=[[Captain (association football)|Vice-captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=22|nat=ESP|name=[[Nacho (footballer, born 1989)|Nacho]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=23|nat=ESP|name=[[Waldo Rubio]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs player|no=24|nat=ESP|name=[[Joaqu\u00edn Fern\u00e1ndez Moreno|Joaqu\u00edn]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=27|nat=GHA|name=[[Mohammed Salisu]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=31|nat=ECU|name=[[Stiven Plaza]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Reserve team===\n{{main|Real Valladolid Promesas}}\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=28|nat=ESP|name=[[Enrique P\u00e9rez Mu\u00f1oz|Kike P\u00e9rez]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs player|no=29|nat=ESP|name=[[Miguel de la Fuente Escudero|Miguel\u00edn]]|pos=FW}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=34|nat=ESP|name=[[Roberto Corral Garc\u00eda|Roberto Corral]]|pos=DF}}\n{{Fs player|no=35|nat=ESP|name=[[V\u00edctor Garc\u00eda Raja|V\u00edctor Garc\u00eda]]|pos=MF}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n===Out on loan===\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no= \u2014|nat=ESP|name=[[Mois\u00e9s Delgado]]|pos=DF|other=at [[Racing de Santander|Racing Santander]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs player|no= \u2014|nat=ESP|name=[[\u00c1lvaro Aguado]]|pos=MF|other=at [[CD Numancia|Numancia]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs player|no= \u2014|nat=MAR|name=[[Anuar Tuhami]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Panathinaikos F.C.|Panathinaikos]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs player|no= \u2014|nat=MTN|name=[[Moctar Sidi El Hacen|El Hacen]]|pos=MF|other=at [[CD Lugo|Lugo]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no= \u2014|nat=ESP|name=[[Luismi (footballer, born 1992)|Luismi]]|pos=MF|other=at [[Real Oviedo|Oviedo]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs player|no= \u2014|nat=ESP|name=[[Christopher Ramos de la Flor|Chris Ramos]]|pos=FW|other=at [[CD Badajoz|Badajoz]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs player|no= \u2014|nat=BRA|name=[[Marcos Andr\u00e9]]|pos=FW|other=at [[CD Mirand\u00e9s|Mirand\u00e9s]] until 30 June 2020}}\n{{Fs player|no= \u2014|nat=SEN|name=[[Sekou Gassama]]